Add embeddings to index vs.upsert_embeddings(index_name="my_index", embeddings=embeddings, ids=ids)
Query the index results = vs.query(index_name="my_index", query_vector=query_embedding)
Search with text input results = vs.query(index_name="my_index", query_text="What is Databricks?")
Delete index vs.delete_index(index_name="my_index")
